videos.description: Sophie Cunningham knocks down a contested 3-pointer in the first quarter for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Missouri's Cunningham drills 3-pointer

videos.description: Sophie Cunningham dribbles by her defender along the baseline and drops in a right-handed layup in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Mizzou's Cunningham runs baseline for score

videos.description: Cierra Porter connects with Sophie Cunningham who knocks in a 3-pointer to give Missouri the lead in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Cunningham's big triple electrifies Missouri crowd

videos.description: Anastasia Hayes drives down the middle of the lane, scores a layup and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Hayes makes crucial 3-point play for Tennessee

videos.description: Missouri's Sophie Cunningham scores 12 of her 32 points in the fourth quarter to propel the No. 13 Tigers to a 77-73 win over No. 11 Tennessee.
videos.headline: Cunningham leads Mizzou past Vols
